name: CUSTOM DESIGN PARTY PRINTABLES - SET OF 8
description:
Made to your specifications, can do almost any design for any type of party from children's to adults, tea parties, hens nights, baby showers and more.

Choose 8 items from the following list:
* Invitation - 6 x 4 inch (std photo size) 
* cupcake toppers 2 inch circles - 2 different designs
* cupcake wrappers - 2 different designs
* buffet cards - 2 different styles & up to 4 different wordings
* water bottle labels - 2 different wordings (9 x 2.5 inch)
* wall bunting - up to 20 letters
* thank you/lolly bag tags - 2 different styles
* chocolate wrappers (9 x 6 inch) for 100g Cadbury or lindt choc 
* A4 wall art 
* matching t-shirt iron on transfer
* sweet bags - 2 different designs (front & back) (7.5 x 5 inch)
* pillow box (6 x 3.5 inch)
* party hat

extra items can be purchased separately.

Please have a peek at my pre-made party printables to get an idea of what each item looks like :)

Once payment has been received you will be sent a list of questions regarding your design choice.  I can also be contacted through my facebook page via the messages which may be easier.

As this is a printable product you will receive a high resolution zipped jpg file via email once the design is completed to your satisfaction.  Printables are best printed on glossy paper and printed colour can vary from colour pictured depending on monitor or printer.

Items may not be shared, sold or re-distributed in any way, shape or form.

If on the rare occasion I cannot come up with a design to your liking I reserve the right to retain 30% of the amount paid with the balance being refunded back through paypal.

name: REINDEER FOOD - CHRISTMAS PRINTABLE BAG LABEL/TAGS
description:
This is another excellent idea for school class gifts .... all you need is 1 tablespoon of crushed oats and 1/4 teaspoon each of red & green glitter in each bag.

If you choose the printed & posted option you will get 30 tags (5 pages with 6 tags to a page printed on 180gsm GLOSS A4 paper) which will be posted to you as a flat pack to be cut out and assembled by you, also included are 30 plastic bags to match.

Each tag measures 8x8 cms. 

If you choose to have the file emailed they are designed to print out with 6 on the page (A4 or US letter).  Plastic bags can be purchased on ebay or packaging stores and need to be 8cms wide and at least 12cms long.

They can be personalised with the givers name only in the from section. 

Printing service available see other option below (Australia only)
